snippet.title: Guitar Hero Live -  Official GHTV Trailer | PS4, PS3
snippet.description:
Introducing GHTV – the world’s first playable music video network. Play hundreds of music videos from GHTV’s continually updating library, compete with friends online, and unlock premium content. Only available on Guitar Hero Live. Coming October 20, 2015.

http://www.guitarhero.com

© 2015 Activision Publishing, Inc. ACTIVISION, FREESTYLEGAMES, GUITAR HERO, and GH are trademarks of Activision Publishing, Inc. All other trademarks and trade names are properties of their respective owners. Activision makes no guarantees regarding the availability of online play or features, including without limitation GHTV, and may modify or discontinue online services in its discretion without notice. Online play such as GHTV requires broadband internet connection. Guitar references are to the Guitar Hero guitar controller.
